<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Verification</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Hello {{userFirstName}},</h1>
    <p>Thank you for registering for <strong>{{eventName}}</strong> at <strong>{{collegeName}}</strong>!</p>
    <p>Please confirm your email address by clicking the link below:</p>
    <p><a href="{{verificationLink}}">Verify Email Address</a></p>
    <p>If you did not register for this event, please ignore this email.</p>
    <h4>Event Details:</h4>
    <p>📅 Event Date: {{eventDate}}</p>
    <p>📍 Location: {{venue}}</p>
    <p>⏰ Time: {{startTime}} to {{endTime}}</p>
</body>
</html>